msgstr "<strong>ຕໍ່ 100 ກຣາມ</strong>"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use case</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ກໍລະນີຕົວຢ່າງ</strong>"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A good practice might be to keep those forecasts up to date for the coming "
"months with\n"
"          your sales, so that the manufacturing team plans at best the "
"production at all time\n"
"          accordingly!"
msgstr ""
"ແນວທາງການປະຕິບັດທີ່ດີຄືການປັບປຸງການຄາດຄະເນໃຫ້ເປັນປັດຈຸບັນສຳລັບເດືອນຕໍ່ໆໄປຕາມ\n"
"          ຍອດຂາຍຂອງທ່ານ, ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທີມງານຜະລິດສາມາດວາງແຜນການຜະລິດໃຫ້ດີທີ່ສຸດຢູ່ສະເໝີ\n"
"          ໃຫ້ສອດຄ່ອງກັນ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Activate the Food &amp; Drinks Labels settings in the Food Distribution "
"section."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ ສະຫຼາກອາຫານ &amp; ເຄື່ອງດື່ມ ໃນສ່ວນ ການກະຈາຍອາຫານ (Food Distribution)."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:food_distribution.field_x_nutritional_facts_active
msgid "Active"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ງານ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add some Salt and Sugar to secure suppliers for longer on those sides."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມເກືອ ແລະ ນ້ຳຕານ ເພື່ອຈັດຫາຜູ້ສະໜອງໃນໄລຍະຍາວສຳລັບລາຍການເຫຼົ່ານີ້."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:x_nutritional_facts,x_name:food_distribution.x_nutritional_facts_4
msgid "Added Sugar"
msgstr "ນ້ຳຕານທີ່ເພີ່ມເຂົ້າ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"All Manufacturing Orders here are Ready to manufacture by default but you "
"can play with\n"
"        the filters at top right of the screen to see them all."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດທັງໝົດໃນນີ້ແມ່ນຢູ່ໃນສະຖານະ ພ້ອມທີ່ຈະຜະລິດ ແຕ່ທ່ານສາມາດນຳໃຊ້\n"
"        ຕົວຕອງຢູ່ມຸມຂວາເທິງຂອງໜ້າຈໍເພື່ອເບິ່ງທັງໝົດ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Also order the Mayonnaise so you can fill those buckets with sauce."
msgstr "ສັ່ງຊື້ ມາຢອນເນສ (Mayonnaise) ຕື່ມອີກ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດບັນຈຸລົງໃນຖັງໄດ້."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.x_nutritional_facts_search_view
msgid "Archived"
msgstr "ຈັດເກັບແລ້ວ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As an Inventory Manager you need to make sure that the production team never "
"runs out of\n"
"          supply!"
msgstr ""
"ໃນນາມຜູ້ຈັດການສາງ, ທ່ານຕ້ອງຮັບປະກັນວ່າທີມງານຜະລິດຈະມີ\n"
"          ວັດຖຸດິບພຽງພໍຢູ່ສະເໝີ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.food_distribution_inherit_report_lot_label
msgid "B.b."
msgstr "ຄວນບໍລິໂພກກ່ອນ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Between production and deliveries, by default, the product picking is "
"organized in FIFO."
msgstr ""
"ລະຫວ່າງການຜະລິດ ແລະ ການສົ່ງມອບ, ໂດຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ການເບີກສິນຄ້າແມ່ນຖືກຈັດລຽງແບບ FIFO (ມາກ່ອນ, "
"ອອກກ່ອນ)."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_9
msgid "Bucket 5L"
msgstr "ຖັງ 5 ລິດ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products, sale\n"
"      orders and more."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍການໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງຂອງໂມດູນນີ້, ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານຈະຖືກເພີ່ມດ້ວຍສິນຄ້າບາງຢ່າງ, ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ\n"
"      ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.res_config_settings_form_view_inherited
msgid ""
"Capture food and drink data on product and leverage them in printed labels."
msgstr "ບັນທຶກຂໍ້ມູນອາຫານ ແລະ ເຄື່ອງດື່ມໃນຕົວສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ນຳໃຊ້ພວກມັນໃນສະຫຼາກທີ່ພິມອອກມາ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:x_nutritional_facts,x_name:food_distribution.x_nutritional_facts_3
msgid "Carbohydrates"
msgstr "ຄາໂບໄຮເດຣດ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click on one of the Ready orders to produce some Mayonnaise."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດທີ່ ພ້ອມແລ້ວ ເພື່ອເລີ່ມຜະລິດ ມາຢອນເນສ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Close Production button at the end of the tile when done with all "
"steps. Great\n"
"        you manufactured you first Mayonnaise batch!"
msgstr ""
"ຄລິກປຸ່ມ ປິດການຜະລິດ ເມື່ອສຳເລັດທຸກຂັ້ນຕອນ. ຍິນດີດ້ວຍ!\n"
"        ທ່ານໄດ້ຜະລິດ ມາຢອນເນສ ຊຸດທຳອິດແລ້ວ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Confirm the Purchase Order when in agreement with your supplier."
msgstr "ຢືນຢັນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ ເມື່ອຕົກລົງກັບຜູ້ສະໜອງຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Confirm the order to close your deal."
msgstr "ຢືນຢັນການສັ່ງຊື້ເພື່ອປິດການຕົກລົງ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create an Invoice, send it to your customer and confirm it to get paid for "
"your hard work!"
msgstr "ສ້າງໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້, ສົ່ງໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າ ແລະ ຢືນຢັນເພື່ອຮັບເງິນຄ່າຕອບແທນຈາກການເຮັດວຽກຂອງທ່ານ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Define dates to plan those smaller orders along the corresponding period to "
"smoothen the\n"
"        load and then proceed to the split.<br/>As a result, the initial "
"order has been split into\n"
"        multiple smaller orders."
msgstr ""
"ກຳນົດວັນທີເພື່ອວາງແຜນໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດຍ່ອຍໆເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນຕາມໄລຍະເວລາທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້\n"
"        ວຽກບໍ່ໜັກເກີນໄປ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນຈຶ່ງດຳເນີນການແຍກ.<br/>ຜົນທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບຄື "
"ໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຈະຖືກແຍກອອກເປັນ\n"
"        ຫຼາຍໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດຍ່ອຍ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.food_distribution_inherit_report_lot_label
msgid "Demo Lot/SN"
msgstr "ເລກລັອດ/ຊີຣຽວ ຕົວຢ່າງ"

