#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Near its name, click the gear icon and select the split option.<br/>Define "
"the Max Batch\n"
"        Size to correspond typically to the packaging of a Mayonnaise tank, "
"35 buckets in for\n"
"        example."
msgstr ""
"ຢູ່ໃກ້ກັບຊື່ຂອງມັນ, ຄລິກທີ່ໄອຄອນຮູບຟັນເຟືອງ ແລະ ເລືອກຕົວເລືອກ ແຍກ (split).<br/>ກຳນົດ "
"ຂະໜາດຊຸດສູງສຸດ\n"
"        ໃຫ້ສອດຄ່ອງກັບການບັນຈຸ ມາຢອນເນສ ຈາກຖັງໃຫຍ່, ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ 35 ຖັງຍ່ອຍ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"No worries, simply increase the Replenishment for a product packaging "
"Mayonnaise to grow\n"
"          the indirect demand of Mayonnaise just below your Actual "
"Replenishment.<br/>This way, you\n"
"          make sure to package all you can, to deliver your customers "
"according to your forecast,\n"
"          and have some buffer to start from next month."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ຕ້ອງກັງວົນ, ພຽງແຕ່ເພີ່ມການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ (Replenishment) ສຳລັບການບັນຈຸ ມາຢອນເນສ ເພື່ອເພີ່ມ\n"
"          ຄວາມຕ້ອງການທາງອ້ອມຂອງ ມາຢອນເນສ ໃຫ້ຢູ່ລຸ່ມການເຕີມສິນຄ້າຕົວຈິງຂອງທ່ານ.<br/"
">ດ້ວຍວິທີນີ້, ທ່ານ\n"
"          ຈະໝັ້ນໃຈໄດ້ວ່າໄດ້ບັນຈຸທຸກຢ່າງທີ່ເຮັດໄດ້, ເພື່ອສົ່ງໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຕາມການຄາດຄະເນ,\n"
"          ແລະ ມີສ່ວນສຳຮອງເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໃນເດືອນຖັດໄປ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now Send the Request For Quotation to your supplier if willing to iterate on "
"price for\n"
"        example."
msgstr ""
"ບັດນີ້ໃຫ້ສົ່ງ ໃບຂໍໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ (RFQ) ໃຫ້ກັບຜູ້ສະໜອງຂອງທ່ານ ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການຕໍ່ຮອງລາຄາ\n"
"        ຕົວຢ່າງ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Now come back to the Sale Order which you can bill since delivered."
msgstr "ບັດນີ້ໃຫ້ກັບຄືນໄປທີ່ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ໄດ້ແລ້ວເນື່ອງຈາກສົ່ງເຄື່ອງແລ້ວ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now come back to the list of manufacturing orders and open the Gantt view "
"from the top right hand side"
msgstr "ບັດນີ້ໃຫ້ກັບຄືນໄປທີ່ລາຍການໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດ ແລະ ເປີດເບິ່ງແບບ Gantt ຈາກມຸມຂວາເທິງ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now let's see how spread the work load from the resulting manufacturing "
"orders."
msgstr "ບັດນີ້ເຮົາມາເບິ່ງວິທີການກະຈາຍພາລະວຽກຈາກໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບ."

