msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo ມອບຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ບໍ່ມີສິ້ນສຸດໃຫ້ທ່ານ ເຊັ່ນ:"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to\n"
"      add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນ, ນີ້ແມ່ນພຽງແຕ່ພາບລວມຂອງຄຸນສົມບັດທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນແພັກເກັດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດ\n"
"      ເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ/ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ, ແລະ ທົດລອງທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມສະບາຍ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On the Vinager Replenishment rule, hit the Order button. This creates a "
"Purchase Order for\n"
"        this product according to the min and max input, which you can edit. "
"Hit the Order button\n"
"        for\n"
"        Mustard while you're here to add those items to the recent Purchase "
"Order."
msgstr ""
"ໃນກົດການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ ນ້ຳສົ້ມສາຍຊູ (Vinegar), ໃຫ້ກົດປຸ່ມ ສັ່ງຊື້ (Order). ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ສຳລັບ\n"
"        ສິນຄ້ານີ້ຕາມຄ່າຕ່ຳສຸດ ແລະ ສູງສຸດທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້, ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້. ກົດປຸ່ມ ສັ່ງຊື້\n"
"        ສຳລັບ ມັດສະຕາດ (Mustard) ໃນຂະນະທີ່ທ່ານຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້ເພື່ອເພີ່ມລາຍການເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນເຂົ້າໃນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຫຼ້າສຸດ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"One last step prior billing with the <strong>Invoicing App</strong>, "
"delivering!"
msgstr "ຂັ້ນຕອນສຸດທ້າຍກ່ອນການເກັບເງິນດ້ວຍ <strong>ແອັບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້</strong>, ກໍ່ຄືການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open one of the finished product and navigate to the Inventory tab."
msgstr "ເປີດສິນຄ້າສຳເລັດຮູບອັນໃດອັນໜຶ່ງ ແລະ ໄປທີ່ແຖບ ສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory)."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Purchase App </strong>and the recently created Purchase "
"Order."
msgstr "ເປີດ <strong>ແອັບການຈັດຊື້ </strong> ແລະ ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ຫາສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃໝ່."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Master Production Schedule from the Planning menu.<br/>Don't panic, "
"this will become\n"
"        your best buddy to optimize your production!"
msgstr ""
"ເປີດ ຕາຕະລາງການຜະລິດຫຼັກ (Master Production Schedule) ຈາກເມນູ ການວາງແຜນ "
"(Planning).<br/>ບໍ່ຕ້ອງຕົກໃຈ, ນີ້ຈະກາຍເປັນ\n"
"        ຕົວຊ່ວຍທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດຂອງທ່ານໃນການເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບການຜະລິດ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Mayonnaise Bucket for example since packaging such a quantity may "
"not happen in\n"
"        one day."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດ ມາຢອນເນສ ແບບຖັງ ເປັນຕົວຢ່າງ ເນື່ອງຈາກການບັນຈຸໃນປະລິມານດັ່ງກ່າວອາດຈະບໍ່ສຳເລັດໃນ\n"
"        ມື້ດຽວ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Replenishment from Operations menu."
msgstr "ເປີດ ການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ (Replenishment) ຈາກເມນູ ການດຳເນີນງານ (Operations)."

