"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບເວັບໄຊ </font>\n"
"        </strong> ແລະ <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບ CRM</font>\n"
"        </strong>!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
