msgstr "ນ້ຳມັນດອກຕາເວັນ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Take advantage of the power of <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Manufacturing App</font>\n"
"        </strong> with Manufacture To\n"
"        Order (MTO) capabilities."
msgstr ""
"ນຳໃຊ້ປະສິດທິພາບຂອງ <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການຜະລິດ</font>\n"
"        </strong> ດ້ວຍຄວາມສາມາດໃນການຜະລິດ\n"
"        ຕາມຄຳສັ່ງ (Manufacture To Order - MTO)."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Bill of Material is accessible from the Manufacturing App Products menu."
msgstr "ລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (Bill of Material) ສາມາດເຂົ້າເບິ່ງໄດ້ຈາກເມນູ ສິນຄ້າ ໃນແອັບການຜະລິດ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Dates section allows you to detail the expiration dates of your products."
msgstr "ສ່ວນ ວັນທີ ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດລະບຸລາຍລະອຽດວັນໝົດອາຍຸຂອງສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານໄດ້."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Mixing tank work center is configured with setup and cleanup time. Take "
"advantage of\n"
"          this capability to optimize your operations!"
msgstr ""
"ສູນວຽກງານຖັງປະສົມ (Mixing tank work center) ຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ມີເວລາໃນການຈັດຕຽມ ແລະ "
"ທຳຄວາມສະອາດ. ນຳໃຊ້\n"
"          ຄວາມສາມາດນີ້ເພື່ອເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບການດຳເນີນງານຂອງທ່ານ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The nutritional fact list is available from the Inventory App, Configuration "
"menu."
msgstr "ລາຍການຂໍ້ມູນໂພຊະນາການສາມາດເຂົ້າເບິ່ງໄດ້ຈາກເມນູ ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ ໃນແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The products from the Replenishment Rules you triggered are here but not all "
"products have\n"
"        Replenishment Rules at this stage. For some products or other "
"suppliers you need, you can\n"
"        chose to add them manually to a Purchase Order and even create new "
"Purchase Orders."
msgstr ""
"ສິນຄ້າຈາກກົດການເຕີມສິນຄ້າທີ່ທ່ານເປີດໃຊ້ແມ່ນຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້ ແຕ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນທຸກສິນຄ້າທີ່ຈະມີ\n"
"        ກົດການເຕີມສິນຄ້າໃນຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້. ສຳລັບບາງສິນຄ້າ ຫຼື ຜູ້ສະໜອງອື່ນໆທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ, ທ່ານສາມາດ\n"
"        ເລືອກເພີ່ມພວກມັນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງເຂົ້າໃນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ ຫຼື ແມ່ນແຕ່ສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໃໝ່."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"There is some stock of Buckets and Dispensers so no need to order some for "
"the ongoing\n"
"        period.<br/>However, you need to order Mayonnaise Buckets to meet "
"your forecast!"
msgstr ""
"ມີສະຕັອກຂອງຖັງ ແລະ ເຄື່ອງຈ່າຍບາງສ່ວນແລ້ວ ດັ່ງນັ້ນຈຶ່ງບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງສັ່ງຊື້ຕື່ມໃນໄລຍະ\n"
"        ນີ້.<br/>ແນວໃດກໍ່ຕາມ, ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງສັ່ງຊື້ ມາຢອນເນສ ແບບຖັງ "
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເປັນໄປຕາມການຄາດຄະເນ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"There now is a smart button at the top of the Purchase Order to reach the "
"associated\n"
"        delivery. Hit the Deliveries smart button to open the delivery."
msgstr ""
"ຕອນນີ້ມີປຸ່ມລັດຢູ່ດ້ານເທິງຂອງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ເພື່ອໄປຫາການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງ\n"
"        ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ. ກົດປຸ່ມລັດ ການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງ ເພື່ອເປີດເບິ່ງການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr "ທັງໝົດນີ້ແມ່ນໃຊ້ໄດ້ຟຣີໃນການສະໝັກໃຊ້ປັດຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານ; ເຊີນສຳຫຼວດໄດ້ເລີຍ! 🙃"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This is great but you might be producing more Mayonnaise than you planned to "
"package..."
msgstr "ນີ້ແມ່ນເລື່ອງທີ່ດີ ແຕ່ທ່ານອາດຈະຜະລິດ ມາຢອນເນສ ຫຼາຍກວ່າທີ່ທ່ານວາງແຜນຈະບັນຈຸ..."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To save time and prevent mistake of typo in the Lot inputs, you might want "
"to work with <strong>Barcode\n"
"          App</strong>!"
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອປະຢັດເວລາ ແລະ ປ້ອງກັນຄວາມຜິດພາດໃນການພິມເລກລັອດ, ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການນຳໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບ\n"
"          ບາໂຄດ</strong>!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.res_config_settings_form_view_inherited
msgid "Traceability"
msgstr "ການຕິດຕາມຄືນ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:food_distribution.field_x_nutritional_facts_unit
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:food_distribution.field_x_product_template_nutritional_fact_unit
msgid "Unit"
msgstr "ຫົວໜ່ວຍ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Maintenance App</font>\n"
"        </strong> to keep all your work\n"
"        centers up and running."
msgstr ""
"ນຳໃຊ້ <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບບຳລຸງຮັກສາ</font>\n"
"        </strong> ເພື່ອໃຫ້ສູນວຽກງານທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານ\n"
"        ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານຢູ່ສະເໝີ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Validate the delivery to your customer to complete the job."
msgstr "ຢືນຢັນການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າເພື່ອສຳເລັດວຽກ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_4
msgid "Vinegar"
msgstr "ນ້ຳສົ້ມສາຍຊູ (Vinegar)"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When hovering the on the Order button for a product Replenishment, a cell is "
"highlighted.\n"
"        Clicking this button orders the corresponding product for that "
"period according to the\n"
"        Replenishment input.<br/>This creates a manufacturing order or a "
"purchase order depending\n"
"        on the product configuration."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອເອົາມາວກາຍປຸ່ມ ສັ່ງຊື້ ສຳລັບການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ, ຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນຈະຖືກເນັ້ນ.\n"
"        ການຄລິກປຸ່ມນີ້ຈະສັ່ງຊື້ສິນຄ້າທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງສຳລັບໄລຍະເວລານັ້ນຕາມທີ່ລະບຸໃນ\n"
"        ການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ.<br/>ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດ ຫຼື ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ ຂຶ້ນກັບ\n"
"        ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When the truck arrives and you add those to your stock, validate the "
"delivery to update\n"
"        your stock levels. Don't forget to set the Lot reference in the "
"details of the delivery\n"
"        lines. You're now ready to product Mayonnaise for some time!"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອລົດຂົນສົ່ງມາຮອດ ແລະ ທ່ານເພີ່ມສິນຄ້າເຂົ້າໃນສະຕັອກ, ໃຫ້ຢືນຢັນການຮັບເຄື່ອງເພື່ອອັບເດດ\n"
"        ລະດັບສະຕັອກຂອງທ່ານ. ຢ່າລືມກຳນົດເລກລັອດອ້າງອີງໃນລາຍລະອຽດຂອງລາຍການ\n"
"        ການຮັບເຄື່ອງ. ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານພ້ອມແລ້ວທີ່ຈະຜະລິດ ມາຢອນເນສ ໄປອີກໄລຍະໜຶ່ງ!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Whether you want to plan your production based on existing sales orders, or "
"based on a\n"
"      forecast, you can use the master production schedule from the "
"<strong>Manufacturing App</strong>\n"
"      ."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ວ່າທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງການວາງແຜນການຜະລິດໂດຍອີງຕາມໃບສັ່ງຂາຍທີ່ມີຢູ່, ຫຼື ອີງຕາມການ\n"
"      ຄາດຄະເນ, ທ່ານສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ຕາຕະລາງການຜະລິດຫຼັກຈາກ <strong>ແອັບການຜະລິດ</strong>\n"
"      ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While you are using <strong>Inventory App</strong>, open the product catalog "
"from the\n"
"        Products menu. This gives you a more comprehensive view of the "
"different products you\n"
"        manipulate."
msgstr ""
"ໃນຂະນະທີ່ທ່ານກຳລັງໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ</strong>, ໃຫ້ເປີດເບິ່ງລາຍການສິນຄ້າຈາກ\n"
"        ເມນູ ສິນຄ້າ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເຫັນພາບລວມທີ່ຊັດເຈນຂຶ້ນຂອງສິນຄ້າຕ່າງໆທີ່ທ່ານ\n"
"        ຈັດການ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Working on your pricing to optimize your margin? You leverage the \"Compute "
"Price from\n"
"          BoM\" action available from the Product form or any Products list."
msgstr ""
"ກຳລັງປັບລາຄາເພື່ອໃຫ້ໄດ້ກຳໄລທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດບໍ? ທ່ານສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ \"ຄຳນວນລາຄາຈາກ\n"
"          BoM\" ທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນແບບຟອມສິນຄ້າ ຫຼື ລາຍການສິນຄ້າໃດໆ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ລົງເລິກຕື່ມອີກບໍ?"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are ready to sign your first customers? To do so, open the Sales App, "
"create a new\n"
"        order and the customer."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານພ້ອມແລ້ວບໍທີ່ຈະເຊັນສັນຍາກັບລູກຄ້າຄົນທຳອິດ? ເພື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ເປີດແອັບການຂາຍ, ສ້າງໃບສັ່ງ\n"
"        ຂາຍໃໝ່ ແລະ ສ້າງຂໍ້ມູນລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງແລ້ວໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢູ່ໜ້າຈໍຫຼັກ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily maintain from here for each product its list of ingredients, "
"the nutritional facts and specific notes to add to the label."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການລາຍການສ່ວນປະກອບ, ຂໍ້ມູນໂພຊະນາການ ແລະ "
"ໝາຍເຫດສະເພາະທີ່ຈະເພີ່ມໃສ່ສະຫຼາກສຳລັບແຕ່ລະສິນຄ້າໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍຈາກບ່ອນນີ້."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now hurry to manufacture the needed products, deliver them prior "
"sending the invoice\n"
"      to bill your customer."
msgstr ""
"ບັດນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດຮີບຜະລິດສິນຄ້າທີ່ຕ້ອງການ, ສົ່ງມອບພວກມັນກ່ອນທີ່ຈະສົ່ງໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້\n"
"      ເພື່ອເກັບເງິນຈາກລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that the replenishment for the Mayonnaise comes as multiple of "
"the batch\n"
"          size. You can adjust this editing the Mayonnaise Production "
"Schedule from the pen icon\n"
"          near its name."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນໄດ້ວ່າການເຕີມສິນຄ້າສຳລັບ ມາຢອນເນສ ຈະມາເປັນຈຳນວນເທົ່າຂອງຂະໜາດ\n"
"          ຊຸດການຜະລິດ. ທ່ານສາມາດປັບປ່ຽນສິ່ງນີ້ໄດ້ໂດຍການແກ້ໄຂ ຕາຕະລາງການຜະລິດມາຢອນເນສ "
"ຈາກໄອຄອນຮູບບິກ\n"
"          ຢູ່ໃກ້ກັບຊື່ຂອງມັນ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see the forecast clicking the chart icon. Down below, you can see "
"that this is\n"
"          the\n"
"          outcome of all the planned Manufacturing Orders..."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເບິ່ງການຄາດຄະເນໄດ້ໂດຍຄລິກທີ່ໄອຄອນຮູບກຣາບ. ຢູ່ດ້ານລຸ່ມ, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນວ່ານີ້ແມ່ນ\n"
"          ຜົນ\n"
"          ທີ່ໄດ້ຈາກໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດທີ່ວາງແຜນໄວ້ທັງໝົດ..."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see you're about to get low on Vinegar and Mustard in the Forecast."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນໄດ້ໃນການຄາດຄະເນວ່າ ນ້ຳສົ້ມສາຍຊູ ແລະ ມັດສະຕາດ ຂອງທ່ານກຳລັງຈະໜ້ອຍລົງ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can setup your Bill of Material to reflect on you production processes "
"with or\n"
"          without steps, with embedded quality checks like in this example "
"or after a production."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (Bill of Material) ໃຫ້ສອດຄ່ອງກັບຂັ້ນຕອນການຜະລິດຂອງທ່ານ "
"ບໍ່ວ່າຈະມີ\n"
"          ຫຼື ບໍ່ມີຂັ້ນຕອນ, ໂດຍມີການກວດສອບຄຸນນະພາບໃນຕົວຄືກັບຕົວຢ່າງນີ້ ຫຼື ກວດສອບຫຼັງການຜະລິດ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo\n"
"          setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ສຳເລັດກໍລະນີຕົວຢ່າງແລ້ວ! ຍັງມີອີກຫຼາຍລ້ານວິທີໃນການປັບແຕ່ງ Odoo\n"
"          ຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງທຸລະກິດ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt; Upgrade\n"
"          your Food Distribution package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງບໍ? ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້. ໄປທີ່ ແອັບ (Apps) &gt; ອຸດສາຫະກຳ "
"(Industries) &gt; ອັບເກຣດ\n"
"          ແພັກເກັດ ການກະຈາຍອາຫານ (Food Distribution) ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ "
"ໝາຍຕິກໃສ່ຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for <strong>Food distribution</strong> package. "
"By doing so, we\n"
"      have installed a bunch of necessary apps to run your business "
"efficiently."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຫາໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງແພັກເກັດ Odoo ສຳລັບ <strong>ການກະຈາຍອາຫານ (Food distribution)</"
"strong>. ການເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ,\n"
"      ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງແອັບທີ່ຈຳເປັນຈຳນວນໜຶ່ງເພື່ອໃຫ້ທຸລະກິດຂອງທ່ານດຳເນີນໄປຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You might have tested this package with or without demo data. In any case, "
"you may have\n"
"      written records in journals which are not deletable and which might be "
"an issue for your\n"
"      traceability."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະໄດ້ທົດລອງໃຊ້ແພັກເກັດນີ້ໂດຍມີ ຫຼື ບໍ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ. ບໍ່ວ່າໃນກໍລະນີໃດກໍ່ຕາມ, ທ່ານອາດຈະມີ\n"
"      ການບັນທຶກລົງໃນບັນຊີປະຈຳວັນ (journals) ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບໄດ້ ແລະ ອາດຈະເປັນບັນຫາສຳລັບ\n"
"      ການຕິດຕາມຄືນຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You registered your first lot of Mayonnaise. Note that it is possible to "
"change the lot\n"
"          number prefix from the product form, in the Inventory tab."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ລົງທະບຽນ ມາຢອນເນສ ລັອດທຳອິດຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ. ໝາຍເຫດ: ທ່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນຄຳນຳໜ້າເລກ\n"
"          ລັອດໄດ້ຈາກແບບຟອມສິນຄ້າ, ໃນແຖບ ສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory)."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you\n"
"      can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຄວນຈະສາມາດດຳເນີນການຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ເພື່ອເຫັນພາບລວມຂອງຂະບວນການຕ່າງໆທີ່ທ່ານ\n"
"      ສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວດ້ວຍແພັກເກັດນີ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ Odoo."

